  <content>{"copy":"&lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor8\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: 400px; background-image:url('https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/dc34a171-8784-4e76-9d78-27026d9a8693/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; color: white; padding: 60px 0;\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-8 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column;\"&gt; &lt;h1&gt;Empowering Community Learning&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;Connecting nonprofit trainers and community learners through accessible workshops and training sessions designed to foster growth and collaboration.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor2\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: auto; padding: 40px 0;\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-6 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;h2&gt;About Our Mission&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;Our nonprofit platform is dedicated to providing community members with easy access to educational workshops and training programs. We support trainers in delivering impactful sessions while managing participant information and preferences efficiently.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-6 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 6px;\" alt=\"Community trainer leading a workshop\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/c4fe74df-261b-42dd-a5bc-21e07afd1539/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor2\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: auto; padding: 40px 0;\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-4 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 15px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 6px;\" alt=\"Participants engaged in group discussion\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/137c8ac2-2600-49ec-a86a-e31e9dd6bcf3/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;h3&gt;Inclusive Learning&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p&gt;We foster an inclusive environment where learners from all backgrounds can engage, share, and grow together.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-4 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 15px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 6px;\" alt=\"Trainer providing hands-on workshop\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/70d371c6-07e7-4fe6-8e11-f474361e2a6f/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;h3&gt;Expert Trainers&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p&gt;Our network of skilled trainers brings valuable knowledge and practical skills to every session.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-4 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 15px;\"&gt; &lt;img style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 6px;\" alt=\"Participant selecting session preferences\" src=\"https://cdn.hubblecontent.osi.office.net/m365content/publish/19ee9a40-a224-44bd-9316-5be25b58d451/thumbnails/xxlarge.jpg\" /&gt; &lt;h3&gt;Personalized Enrollment&lt;/h3&gt; &lt;p&gt;Participants can easily select sessions that match their interests and needs, ensuring a tailored learning experience.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div data-component-theme=\"portalThemeColor2\" class=\"row sectionBlockLayout\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; min-height: auto; padding: 40px 0;\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"container\"&gt; &lt;div class=\"col-md-12 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;\"&gt; &lt;h2&gt;Join Our Community&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;We invite nonprofits, trainers, and learners to collaborate and build a vibrant community focused on education and empowerment. Together, we can make a lasting impact.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;button class=\"button1\" onclick=\"window.location.href='/enroll'\"&gt;Explore Workshops&lt;/button&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;","enablerating":false,"enabletracking":false,"excludefromsearch":false,"hiddenfromsitemap":false,"sharedpageconfiguration":false,"isroot":false,"rootwebpageid":"3117bdd0-69d1-4289-ac09-f894b459a05e","pagetemplateid":"ab186c9d-1f56-4663-a166-c12fb392dd27","partialurl":"about-us","publishingstateid":"18c9ace9-f280-41b6-897e-0b274144316b","parentpageid":"52fe0cd3-82e7-4784-a468-ccfd4b17ef00"}</content>
